attributes.Long form description: The student removes the battery from the GoPro, puts it back in, removes the sd card, drops the sd card inside the GoPro, inserts it back, turns on the GoPro and then turns it back off, assembles the GoPro into a mount peg, and changes it into a handheld grip, finally disassembles the GoPro from the handheld grip and puts all the parts separately.

attributes.Action sentence: The student removes the battery from the GoPro.
The student inserts the battery into the GoPro.

attributes.Transcription: Now change the micro SD card,

attributes.Action sentence: The student removes the micro SD card from the GoPro.
The student inserts an SD card.
The student turns on their GoPro.
The student turns off their GoPro.
The student assembles the GoPro into the mount.
The student removes the GoPro from the mount.
The students assemble the GoPro into the handheld grip.

attributes.Transcription: And put on the tripod grip.

attributes.Action sentence: The student removes the GoPro from the handheld grip.
